column5: Don't let us down.  Its been a long winter.  A report with pics of fish would help my cabin fever.
I will post a picture of every fish I catch sorry, it might be the shortest topic on record.......LOL I AM HOPING IT LOOKS SOMETHING LIKE THIS
they are all real caught by me over the years
Don't question that , some beauties as well.  I guess I was trying to be funny , its the 'young' Terry I was referring to !LOL  TB
LOL,I missed that  some are more then 2 years agooooooooooooooooooooooo  ah.. top right corner when I had lots of hair where does it go....in my comb I think   how many would you like Bri
pretty cool pic Terry, would make a great puzzle  bottom row, second from the right must be ur son, lol
Sorry Terry, I wasn't clear. I meant 19 or 1880's, not 19 or 18 years old.  Jokes and smart    comments are not as funny in type.
oh God  Lloyd picking on me is spreading through out the forum.......LOL

Ah crap Terry, I thought we were fishin for Specks!!!! Truck is loaded, fishin gear, libation, snacks, clothes, coffee is already made and in the Thermos... just gotta find Terry's house in the morning... might get up half an hour before I go to bed just to be sure... See yah in the morning Terry! HH
Hey Joe. Keep it simple, jig slow.....old school!

Bernie... I was getting my stuff together the other day and all I kept saying to myself was old school! What would Bernie do! I hear yah Bud! Oh and thanks to you, I went out and bought a pair of reading glasses to keep in my boat bag! This gettin old stuff is gettin old already! Thanks Bernie! HH
Terry.. how about posting some photos of trophy sized fish next time.. jeeze..what is this, amateur hour?
I would have to catch them first  I just seem to catch these babies, oh well I put them all back so when they get big I can catch them again
